Write a Terraform code for creating servers in AWS, GCP and Azure if required
	AWS --> Jenkins, inbound - all ports and outbound - 80
	GCP --> Docker
	Azure --> Kubernetes
Install Terraform, Git and Ansible in local machine or in local VM or create each VM for each tool
Once Terraform code is written, commit and push to Github
Once commit is done, automatically Terraform apply should run through Jenkins pipeline and infrastructure should be created for Docker and Kubernetes
Through Ansible create congifute Docker and Kubernetes
Build docker images for application and database
Configure Kubernetes for managing above Docker images and if possible with the help of Kubernetes increate containers for above application

In Ansible server, install AWX and configure the above 3 servers in AWX for patching of these servers through AWX
If required open ports for above servers for patching
